TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {6773=I experimented with several anti artifact software choices before settling on Topaz DeJpeg.  And that it was more that it damaged the images I take the least in doing it's work. I rarely do final images larger than 2048 pixels wide and it works well for me at that. If I very carefully apply my entire PP step chain.  The HX200v definitely depends for good output on good PP techniques compared to my a700 DSLRs.}
